HEADWORD: Cockhead
<hw>Cock"head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mach.)</fld>
<def>The rounded or pointed top of a grinding mill spindle, forming a
pivot on which the stone is balanced.</def>⟦br⟧
